.TH HOPCODERX 1 "HopCoderX local"
.SH NAME
hopcoderx \- AI-powered coding assistant
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hopcoderx
.RI [ options ]
.RI < command >
.RI [ arguments ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
HopCoderX is an AI-powered coding assistant that helps you write, review, and understand code.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-v, \-\-version\fR
Show version number
.TP
\fB\-h, \-\-help\fR
Show help
.TP
\fB\-\-print\-logs\fR
Print logs to stderr
.TP
\fB\-\-log\-level\fR
Set log level (DEBUG, INFO, WARN, ERROR)
.SH COMMAND GROUPS
.TP
\fBsession\fR
Session & TUI
.TP
\fBsetup\fR
Setup & install
.TP
\fBservices\fR
Services & daemons
.TP
\fBdiagnostics\fR
Diagnostics & maintenance
.TP
\fBintegrations\fR
Integrations
.TP
\fBautomation\fR
Automation & workflows
.SH EXAMPLES
.B hopcoderx run "implement user authentication"
.B hopcoderx session list
.B hopcoderx config get model
.B hopcoderx plugins list
.SH SEE ALSO
Full documentation at: https://hopcoder.dev
